### Iegūt visus programmas rezultātus
GET http://localhost:8080/api/programme-results
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūt programmas rezultātu pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/programme-results/{{uuid}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Izveidot jaunu programmas rezultātu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/programme-results
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studyProgram": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "category": {
    "id": "b24ee2f0-b9c5-4cd2-a032-04ae11e6e9cd"
  },
  "language": "lv",
  "learningOutcome": "Spēj izstrādāt vienkāršus algoritmus un programmēt tos izvēlētā valodā"
}

###

### Atjaunināt esošu programmas rezultātu
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/programme-results/{{uuid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studyProgram": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "category": {
    "id": "b24ee2f0-b9c5-4cd2-a032-04ae11e6e9cd"
  },
  "language": "en",
  "learningOutcome": "Able to develop simple algorithms and implement them in a selected programming language"
}

###

### Dzēst programmas rezultātu pēc ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/programme-results/{{uuid}}
